%F A183641 a(n) = 10*a(n-1) - 35*a(n-2) + 50*a(n-3) - 24*a(n-4).
%F A183641 a(n) = 4*4^n + 1530*3^n + 37320*2^n + 223290. - _Christian Krause_, Jun 23 2026
%e A183641 Some solutions for 3 X 9:
%e A183641   2  0  2  2  0  0  3  0  2    0  2  3  0  3  0  2  2  3
